Rodrigo y Gabriela - Southern Ground Music and Food Festival

Performed October 11, 2014, at the Blackbaud Stadium, Charleston, South Carolina

Rodrigo and Gabriela are an acoustic guitar playing husband and wife duo from Mexico. They have a very unique Latin style that is based on, what I would call, New Age Flamenco. Others have described it as Acoustic Heavy Metal. In any case it is definitely Rock And Roll. They are true masters of the guitar and their music is incredible.

They appeared at the Southern Ground Music and Food Festival on Saturday, October 11, 2014. They were the 5th opening act on Saturday and took the stage just as the sun was setting. They have a new album out under their name. Here is a link to their web site:
